title: [unboxing] NEW Intel i7 6850K Broadwell-E X99 Processor - The Streamer's CPU
description:
This is the new Intel i7-6850K. 3.6Ghz Clock with 3.8Ghz Turbo. Unlocked, hexcore (6), 14nm FinFet Technology for the X99 Chipset. It is a great value for performance and utility. 40 CPU lanes allow for maximum bandwidth between GPUs in SLI or Crossfire mode. 
    
Intel i7-6850K $628 from Amazon. | http://amzn.to/1OoiMxG  
  
X99 Motherboards | http://amzn.to/1Pt25vL  
GIGABYTE GA-X99P-SLI | http://amzn.to/1UtUfru  
NVIDIA GTX 1080 for SLI | http://amzn.to/1UyvUg5
